{
    "<p>Banker; art collector.": [],
    "Renders was born as \u00c9mile-L\u00e9on Houvenaeghel.": [],
    "He was adopted by the Bruges antiquarian August-Adolf Renders, receiving the family name Houvenaeghel-Renders, abridged to Renders in 1907.": [],
    "He married Julienne Sylvie D'Hoore (1875-1956).": [
        [
