    "In 1946 ten panels from the collection returned to Brussels.": [],
    "The Belgian <em>Office de R\u00e9cup\u00e9ration \u00e9conomique</em> denied Renders' claims of ownership.": [],
    "In 1949-1951 Renders eventually lost a lawsuit against the Belgian State.": [
